OL,3,CThree charged over multi-million pound
OL,4,Cfraud at prestigious sixth form college
OL,6,FThree people have been charged in
OL,7,Fconnection with a multi-million-pound
OL,8,Ffraud at a leading sixth form college
OL,9,Fin Wales.
OL,11,FSouth Wales Police confirmed it has
OL,12,Fcharged two men and a woman in
OL,13,Fconnection with suspected financial
OL,14,Firregularities at Cardiff Sixth Form
OL,15,FCollege between 2012 and 2016.
OL,17,FNadeem Sarwar, 48, from Pentwyn,
OL,18,FCardiff, and Yasmin Anjum Sarwar, 43,
OL,19,Ffrom Cyncoed, Cardiff, have been
OL,20,Fcharged with multiple theft and fraud
OL,21,Foffences worth around #5million.
